messages.subject_original: Odyssey Import Tariff - February Ex: Feb 1-14th, 2022 Revise
messages.subject_stripped: Odyssey Import Tariff - February Ex: Feb 1-14th, 2022 Revise
messages.body_original:
p class="xpf0">Dear
Valued customer,
Please find
attached an Excel copy of our current IMPORT tariff Revised: Rate ex Singapore or via Singapore to Vancouver
Should
additional services such as below be required, please do not hesitate in
contacting our office directly.
Terminal
to Terminal services across Canada upon arrival
Door
Pickup at Origin and / or door Delivery at destination
Customs
Clearance (Case by case only)
Kindly
contact our customer service representative team for the port you are looking
in to for further information.
N.B.
Should you wish to be removed from our weekly schedule and tariff update, please send us an email
to importquotes@odysseyshipping.com in
order to update your account.
